<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>class <link linkend="_class_d__reg">D_reg</link> provides a single object for a front panel register This is the single 16-bit register displayed on the top row of LEDs. (It can also be used to test the bottom 16 LEDs.) </para>
</section>
